a little self-defense.

204
00:09:35,118 --> 00:09:36,918
Show me what you remember.

205
00:09:37,297 --> 00:09:38,747
Right... right now?

206
00:09:40,798 --> 00:09:41,848
Gosh, uh...

207
00:09:42,819 --> 00:09:44,875
- Thumbs out.
- Thumbs... attaboy.

