for not getting an iPad?

239
00:11:08,638 --> 00:11:11,272
Don't make me sorry
I shared that with you, okay?

240
00:11:11,838 --> 00:11:13,138
See you, fellas.

241
00:11:17,905 --> 00:11:18,905
Howdy do.

242
00:11:19,455 --> 00:11:22,450
